{"tid":2216162,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共嚴審外資 閹割Switch","createTime":"2020-09-24T13:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T13:20:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4907c1978d5374ed00afa955c91e835fa46f7f3d","tid":2216162,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T13:05:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/XK4MXGSY4ZFZ3EONQBRTPUSKSA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FXK4MXGSY4ZFZ3EONQBRTPUSKSA%2F&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=f90759e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FXK4MXGSY4ZFZ3EONQBRTPUSKSA%2F&h=2fbc850b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/XK4MXGSY4ZFZ3EONQBRTPUSKSA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中共嚴審外資 閹割Switch<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/65aNFDrp_1S83Vitu9PUhL_2FaY=/3500x2377/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TRPDNHYB3BDTTOZPKR3WXZBEDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F65aNFDrp_1S83Vitu9PUhL_2FaY%3D%2F3500x2377%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTRPDNHYB3BDTTOZPKR3WXZBEDM.jpg&h=3b67aaaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中國版Switch用戶在大多數遊戲中，都無法經網絡連線接通外國玩家，亦不能在Switch非中國區網絡商店買遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n日本企業為內地帶來大量外資及工作崗位，惟中共為政治因素加強審查及限制外資在華活動；貢獻良多的日企亦未能倖免，一個小小的Switch遊戲機，正是縮影。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：財經專題：累積投資近萬億 聘一千萬員工  兩國關係轉壞 日企謀撤出中國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n玩家掛「武漢肺炎」  動森遭下架<br />\n<br />\nSwitch是日企任天堂2017年推出的遊戲機，具備網絡連接功能，惟之後兩年都未能在內地正式發行；去年找到騰訊做中國代理商，終有正式渠道打入內地市場，卻被要求「閹割」功能。<br />\n<br />\n中國版Switch用戶在大多數遊戲中，都無法經網絡連線接通外國玩家，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n縱然內地人口及市場龐大，任天堂社長今年5月坦承，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n對於涉及網絡審查，中國日本商會在《中國經濟與日本企業2019年白皮書》中反映，。。。。。。"},{"pid":"ba6220d5a0d10f1cbd9f43d625592ebd6b31e1e2","tid":2216162,"uid":85586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T13:08:53.000Z","msg":"小粉紅：任天堂nmsl<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473f8ef2fa6d3bf5076a1dd6de2ceed73e7246c4","tid":2216162,"uid":216694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T13:09:27.000Z","msg":"鎖國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />晚清2.0"},{"pid":"0bfa6f7ea448c7f703ea63d7b5383cd2451743a2","tid":2216162,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T13:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}